{"lexicon" 1, "id" "com.etzhayyim.maps.kg.queryChunk", "defs" {"main" {"type" "query", "description" "Read placed features owning a set of H3 cells, label-filtered — the kotoba-native getChunk hot-path (ADR-2606064500 §2). Resolves per requested cell to an AVET probe AVET(:feature.cell/r{lod}, <cell>) -> subjects, so the read is O(requested cells), never a bbox scan. kotoba-native successor to the legacy maps com.etzhayyim.apps.maps.getChunk (RisingWave vertex_spatial bbox SELECT). The KAMI 3D renderer consumes the returned GeoJSON unchanged.", "parameters" {"type" "params", "required" ["h3Cells" "lod"], "properties" {"h3Cells" {"type" "array", "items" {"type" "string"}, "maxLength" 128, "description" "requested H3 cells at resolution = lod"}, "lod" {"type" "integer", "minimum" 0, "maximum" 15, "description" "H3 resolution; the app's zoom->LOD ladder uses {2,4,6,8,10,12}"}, "labels" {"type" "array", "items" {"type" "string"}, "maxLength" 32, "description" ":feature/label keywords (without colon) to include; default = the 11 render labels"}, "limit" {"type" "integer", "minimum" 1, "maximum" 5000, "default" 500, "description" "per-label per-cell cap"}}}, "output" {"encoding" "application/json", "schema" {"type" "object", "properties" {"chunks" {"type" "unknown", "description" "{ [h3Cell]: { [label]: GeoJSON Feature[] } }"}, "lod" {"type" "integer"}, "total" {"type" "integer"}, "servedBy" {"type" "string", "description" "\"kotoba\" | \"risingwave\" — which substrate served (fail-open transition, §3)"}}}}}}}